    "title": "第1話",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ある日のトレーニング終わり。\r\n後輩と一緒にいるフジキセキを見かけた。",
            "enText": "One day, after training was over. \nI saw Fuji Kiseki with some underclassmen.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 141,
                    "pathId": -1020202840295056446
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6934097733728262588,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "まったく、いけない子だね。\r\n私をこんな、ひと気のないところに呼びだして――",
            "enText": "Goodness, you're awfully naughty. \nYou called me out here, in the middle of nowhere――",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 221,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -762630696860586874
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1675085625345768849,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "どうしたんだい、ポニーちゃん？",
            "enText": "What's the matter, Pony-chan?",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 75,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 9136476019473938630
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7791468987948623542,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "後輩ウマ娘",
            "enName": "Junior Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "あっ、あの、フジ先輩……。",
            "enText": "U, um, Fuji-senpai ……",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 92,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": -1706720994787860824
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3789864466598917338,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "後輩ウマ娘",
            "enName": "Junior Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "今日は、心に決めてきました。\r\n先輩に気持ちを伝えようって……。",
            "enText": "I decided, today. \nI'm going to tell Senpai how I feel about her…",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 172,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 766787776389004926
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6544247382296544650,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "……いいとも。\r\n全身全霊をもって、受け止めさせてもらおう。",
            "enText": "…That's quite alright. \nI'll accept it to the best of my ability.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 250,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 123,
                    "pathId": 7787483207479970921
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -4846164486223004152
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5501314013902612395,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "後輩ウマ娘",
            "enName": "Junior Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "フジ先輩……\r\nあたし、先輩のことが大好きです！",
            "enText": "Fuji-senpai… \nI really like you, Senpai!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 179,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 136,
                    "pathId": -5684991500649756230
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8595762942511233128,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "後輩ウマ娘",
            "enName": "Junior Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "1学年後輩として、先輩の背中をずっと追いかけてきました。\r\nいつか、あの背中に追いついて……そして……。",
            "enText": "As a first grade junior, I've always followed your back, Senpai. \nSomeday, I'll catch up with that back… and then…",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 307,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 336,
                    "pathId": 531520275841283485
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -518550562741474080,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "後輩ウマ娘",
            "enName": "Junior Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "隣に並んで……一緒に……一緒に走るんだ……って。",
            "enText": "We'll stand side by side and… together… together we'll \nrun… I, I thought.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 205,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 189,
                    "pathId": -5783913886689127053
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2821824085999644609,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "君――",
            "enText": "You――",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 39,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 8734483692789017333
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1607527415300223841,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "後輩ウマ娘",
            "enName": "Junior Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "だから……こんなの、あんまりだって……。\r\n悔しくって……。",
            "enText": "That's why… I said this it was too much… \nAnd that I was so frustrated…",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 173,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 137,
                    "pathId": 3326452653428561587
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 37,
                    "pathId": 2233817438076414217
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -15990324791342447,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "――さあ、顔を上げて。",
            "enText": "――Come, lift your chin up.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -1025956155749693404
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 1738038364628621957
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3217381579884711682,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "君が今日で学園を去ること、理事長からうかがっているよ。\r\n……足のケガ、だってね。",
            "enText": "I gathered from the President that you're leaving the Academy \ntoday. \n…She said you have a leg injury.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 252,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 166,
                    "pathId": -3130212816681012345
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 8944791092133710516
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7349213289940362624,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "後輩ウマ娘",
            "enName": "Junior Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "ううっ……。",
            "enText": "Uuugh…",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 62,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": 1277284008638050539
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 59852688645253361,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "君は、後輩の中でもひときわ才能にあふれていた。\r\nいつか、手ごわいライバルになるだろうって。",
            "enText": "You were one of the most talented of the younger class. \nI knew that one day, you would be a formidable rival.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 257,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 249,
                    "pathId": -5223734916004194906
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 153,
                    "pathId": 7018378375957597196
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 680006972176057627,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "なにより、人一倍ひたむきに練習に励んでいただろ？\r\nだから、私も悔しい。",
            "enText": "Above all, you were practicing harder than anyone else, \nweren't you? \nThat's why I'm frustrated, too.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 280,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 115,
                    "pathId": 4025067317528995979
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 56,
                    "pathId": -5703700865477752218
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3420579283256049973,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "私だって、ずっと君を見ていたんだ。",
            "enText": "I've been watching you for all this time, too.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 133,
                    "pathId": -4317421871067558737
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 3159658844974893059
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4749731777487362315,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "後輩ウマ娘",
            "enName": "Junior Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "フジ先輩……！",
            "enText": "Fuji-senpai…!",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 37,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 7508934824690237986
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9201313945185402652,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "後輩ウマ娘",
            "enName": "Junior Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "あたし、もっと走りたかった……。\r\n走り続けて、たくさん勝ち星を上げて、いつか……っ。",
            "enText": "I wanted to run more… \nI wanted to keep running, get lots of wins, and one day…",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 228,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 241,
                    "pathId": 2257774842258307815
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6435894876845889216,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "いつか……。",
            "enText": "One day…",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 39,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -4850999928225017637
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8489408948421651527,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "後輩ウマ娘",
            "enName": "Junior Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "……先輩に、あたしの夢を託してもいいですか？\r\nウマ娘としての、夢を……。",
            "enText": "…Can I entrust my dream to you, Senpai? \nAs an Uma Musume, can I entrust my dream to…",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 258,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 318,
                    "pathId": 7233857765919486320
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4261392602824817867,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "君の気持ち、確かに受け取ったよ。\r\n一緒に走ろう。どこまでも。",
            "enText": "I've most certainly received your feelings. \nLet's run, together. No matter how far.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 205,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 77,
                    "pathId": 7636560238251293373
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 115,
                    "pathId": -1615680163187269260
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5919197244444003113,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "夕焼けに、かすかな泣き声が響く。\r\nやがて後輩は、笑顔を見せて去っていった。",
            "enText": "A faint cry echoed in the evening glow of sunset. \nIn the end, the junior left with a smile on her face.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": -5903063434953047268
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": -768947505422936762
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1672139442413033243,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "どうやら、私の秘密を見られてしまったようだ。\r\nいるんだろう？　トレーナーさん。",
            "enText": "It looks as if you've seen my secret. \nI know you're in there, aren't you? Trainer.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 234,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "気づいてたんだ",
                    "enText": "I noticed.",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 166,
                    "pathId": 6844075733637199136
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": 4826395459501337542
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7701856240604516933,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "……時々、ああして学園を去る子がいてね。\r\n私はどうしようもない無力感に苛まれるんだ。",
            "enText": "…On occasion, there are girls that leave the academy like that. \nI feel tormented by a feeling of utter helplessness.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 332,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 134,
                    "pathId": -1664969652393048046
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -4427267305859702820
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1865973863110930591,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "夢破れてしまった子を、どうしたら楽しませられる？\r\nあんなに寂しげな笑顔をさせてしまった。",
            "enText": "How can I entertain a girl whose dreams have been dashed? \nI made her smile so sadly.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 262,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 251,
                    "pathId": 1683177019850930516
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 7950442091738412446
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2213223664880183991,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "私に『ウマ娘としての夢を託す』――か。",
            "enText": "Entrust me with your dream \"as an Uma Musume\"――so she \nsaid.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 178,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": 9148475844458548017
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6618152207720693649,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――そういえば、フジキセキは以前、役者になる夢を諦めて\r\nレースを選んだと話していた……。",
            "enText": "――Speaking of which, Fuji Kiseki once told me that she gave \nup her dream of becoming an actor and chose racing…",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "君の今の夢は？",
                    "enText": "What's your dream, right now?",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "貴方の今の夢は？",
                    "enText": "What's your dream, right now?",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 132,
                    "pathId": 5735443381293202079
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8597243768533561757,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "私の夢？　それはもちろん、\r\n『“キセキ”を起こし、みんなを楽しませること』――",
            "enText": "My dream? That, of course, is to \"Make \"Miracles\" happen, \nand to entertain all.\"――",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 266,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -641798256224113669
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": 4643069398962751413
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8247343804223375686,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "だが……そう言うなり、フジキセキは押し黙ってしまった。\r\nなにか、考え込むような表情を浮かべて。",
            "enText": "But… as soon as she said that, Fuji Kiseki fell silent. \nA sort of thoughtful expression appeared on her face.",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……大丈夫？",
                    "enText": "…Are you alright?",
                    "nextBlock": 31
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 149,
                    "pathId": 862345620023032252
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 128,
                    "pathId": -8601646846100959375
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7474411267511469501,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "おっと、いけないいけない。\r\n“フジキセキ”は、こんな時こそ笑わなくてはね！",
            "enText": "Whoops, that's no good, no good at all. \nIt's at times like this that \"Fuji Kiseki\" must laugh!",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 209,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": 135634982343486856
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 38,
                    "pathId": 5058407573552877451
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7792356968327007602,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "フジキセキ",
            "enName": "Fuji Kiseki",
            "jpText": "今日見たことは、どうか秘密にしておくれよ。\r\nほら、私と君だけの約束だ――",
            "enText": "Please, keep what you saw today a secret. \nLook, it's just a promise between you and me――",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 262,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 135,
                    "pathId": -4487263683624627975
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4599545845343089956,
            "blockIdx": 32
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "フジキセキは精一杯の笑顔を見せた。",
            "enText": "Fuji Kiseki smiled as best she could.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 87,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 8384407396398159555
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5976736460838507315,
            "blockIdx": 33
        }
    ],
